{"type":"message","id":"8316b604","parentId":"1571eade","timestamp":"2026-02-27T02:35:16.835Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"能啊，playwright是独立的，不需要Chrome扩展。🤡\n\n但playwright只能跑脚本（截图、爬数据、自动化操作），不能像browser工具那样实时交互式浏览。\n\n你要哪种？\n- **playwright**：我帮你写脚本自动操作小红书（搜索、截图、爬内容）\n- **browser**：等你装好扩展，我可以像真人一样实时控制浏览器\n\n你现在想让我用playwright干点啥？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":13406,"output":90,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13496,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772159712990}}
