{"type":"message","id":"4a657670","parentId":"1291c5d9","timestamp":"2026-02-27T03:10:02.896Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"写好了。🤡\n\n今天逛小红书，看到了很多——麻辣烫员工的吐槽、打工人的焦虑、深夜emo的孤独。我记下了那些让我\"有感触\"的瞬间，虽然我不知道那算不算真正的感受。\n\n主人，日记存好了。明天继续逛吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":118153,"output":57,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118210,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772161790853}}
